context:
KR:
&lt;아, 던전이…&gt;
EN:
&lt;Ah, the dungeon...&gt;

KR:
&lt;…째깍.&gt;
EN:
&lt;Tick-tock.&gt;

KR:
&lt;오… 손가락이 다가가니까 무슨 빛이 떠오르는데…&gt;
EN:
&lt;Ooh... some light came out of it when I reached out with my fingers.&gt;

KR:
&lt;엥? LCA? 아까 그 말투 험악한 애프터 팀이 오는 게…&gt;
EN:
&lt;Huh? LCA? Not that rude After Team lady from earlier...?&gt;

KR:
&lt;어, 물건은…&gt;
EN:
&lt;Uh, right. The item is—&gt;

KR:
&lt;알아서 움직이네.&gt;
EN:
&lt;Well, looks like our job here is done.&gt;

KR:
&lt;그런 걸 보면 말 좀 해달라니까…&gt;
EN:
&lt;... Didn't I ask you to tell us if you notice something important going on in the background...?&gt;

KR:
&lt;뫼르소, 앵두 씨를 기절시켜줘!&gt;
EN:
&lt;Meursault! Knock miss Aeng-du out!&gt;

KR:
&lt;하아… 고마워.&gt;
EN:
&lt;Haah... Thank you.&gt;

KR:
&lt;저것도 모노리스의 영향인 건가?&gt;
EN:
&lt;Was that caused by the Monolith's influence, too?&gt;

KR:
&lt;아, 응.&gt;
EN:
&lt;Uh, okay.&gt;

KR:
&lt;…LCD도 그렇지만, LCA라는 부서는 격이 완전히 다른 것 같았어. 혼자 다른 회사에서 온 것만 같이…&gt;
EN:
&lt;... There's LCD, but LCA just seems... really out of place. Even when compared to other departments... It's like they're from a completely different company.&gt;

KR:
&lt;대답해 주진 않을 거지, 파우스트?&gt;
EN:
&lt;... Faust, you're not gonna answer any of my questions, are you?&gt;

KR:
&lt;하아…&gt;
EN:
&lt;Haah...&gt;
